{"tid":1135165,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雅蘭中心酒樓燒油煙槽 濃煙充斥彌敦道途人爭相走避","createTime":"2019-05-02T06:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T06:54:16.000Z","uid":3090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84d1871f0f682d7a627baa78527bb560dc4abf95","tid":1135165,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3VioE7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3VioE7.png&h=3f62f48f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmoLN6O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmoLN6O.png&h=dedff516&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoC1mrP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoC1mrP.png&h=72333ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fMVycyu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfMVycyu.png&h=72d44f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0vY76Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0vY76Q.png&h=59eaefef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角彌敦道639號雅蘭中心，中午1時22分，商場二樓一間酒樓廚房發生火警，大量濃煙冒出商場外，熙來攘往的彌敦道，煙霧瀰漫，當時正值午飯時間，大批途人見狀爭相走避，有人一臉驚惶，掩鼻而過，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n讀者周先生剛在現場行街，突看見商場低層冒出黑煙，並越來越濃，整條彌敦道充斥濃煙，並發出刺鼻氣味，途人爭相走避，部份人更索性走入港鐵站避煙。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，商場酒樓廚房起火，消防出動一喉一煙帽隊，約15分鐘將火救熄，其間無人受傷，初步相信是油煙槽起火，起火原因無可疑。"},{"pid":"a73900936a52f51a89b7d5028d59dad938115897","tid":1135165,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:52:28.000Z","msg":"2047 大限 !"},{"pid":"0ce2c3333426e1bc3aab3bb97692e9c8ab3c315d","tid":1135165,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"有冇烤蝗？"}]}